    INSERT INTO story(id, title, issue_id, synopsis, reprint_notes, notes, type_id) VALUES(62276,"Siege of the Iron Giants", 6174,"Ironsides is the brother of Dr. Psycho as brilliant a geologist as Dr. Psycho and was a hypnotist. Discovering a volcano whose eruptions contained large amounts of molten gold in the Pacific island nation Wooloo he decks himself and his gang in armor and stilts becoming iron giants and himself King Ironsides. Chief Loko requests the aid of Army Intelligence agents to battle the group of iron giants that are kidnapping members of his tribe to mine gold. Wonder Woman exposes the giants as men dressed in iron suits and captured King Ironsides and his men.",NULL,"Writer credit from \"The Secret History of Wonder Woman\" (Jill Lapore 2014) formerly credited to Robert Kanigher.Joye Hummel is the maiden name for the scripter (before 1947) then she married David Murchison. When he passed away Joye married Jack Kelly. So her name all combined reads Joye Hummel Murchison Kelly the way Jill Lapore refers to her in her book above.Note: Hummel resigned from DC in 1947 not long after Marston's death but her stories continued to appear in print into 1949.",19
