    INSERT INTO story(id, title, issue_id, synopsis, reprint_notes, notes, type_id) VALUES(65058,"In The Hands of the Merciless [Part 3]", 6549,"The four remaining members of Villainy Inc. have fled to the man's world with Hippolyte's jewels. These remain hidden until a tip from a shopkeeper leads the Amazon Princess to the criminal's lair where she is captured but later freed by Steve Etta and the Hollidays Girls. The four villains are then taken to Transformation Island.",NULL,"Writer credit from \"The Secret History of Wonder Woman\" (Jill Lapore 2014) previously given as William Moulton Marston.Joye Hummel is the maiden name for the scripter (before 1947) then she married David Murchison. When he passed away Joye married Jack Kelly. So her name all combined reads Joye Hummel Murchison Kelly the way Jill Lapore refers to her in her book above.Note: Hummel resigned from DC in 1947 not long after Marston's death but her stories continued to appear in print into 1949.Oddity: Lapore's book only lists part 2 of the story by Hummel. Printer's error?",19
